  "htmlContent": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><meta name=\"view-transition\" content=\"same-origin\"><!-- Prefetch flow pages for instant navigation -->\n    <link rel=\"prefetch\" href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/dcbb8baf-c311-42eb-8c3b-01359cbbdafc\" as=\"document\">\n    <link rel=\"prefetch\" href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/d2d5d0aa-c669-49b6-9b33-a28441cf4b5d\" as=\"document\">\n    <link rel=\"prefetch\" href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/254e9f8f-72d8-4ce3-a2b9-61b026d05b1e\" as=\"document\">\n    <link rel=\"prefetch\" href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/a44ee394-4e27-4984-95ee-689b5df446b4\" as=\"document\">\n    <title>JOSEOCEANJOBS ΓÇö Empowering Skills, Connecting Worlds</title><script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script><script src=\"https://code.iconify.design/iconify-icon/1.0.7/iconify-icon.min.js\"></script><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><style>html { background-color: #073057; } @view-transition { navigation: auto; } ::view-transition { background-color: #073057; } ::view-transition-old(main-nav), ::view-transition-new(main-nav), ::view-transition-old(main-footer), ::view-transition-new(main-footer), ::view-transition-old(brand-logo), ::view-transition-new(brand-logo) { animation: none; mix-blend-mode: normal; } ::view-transition-old(main-content) { animation: 0.25s ease-out both fade-out; } ::view-transition-new(main-content) { animation: 0.25s ease-in 0.1s both fade-in; } @keyframes fade-out { from { opacity: 1; } to { opacity: 0; } } @keyframes fade-in { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } } ::view-transition-old(root), ::view-transition-new(root) { animation: none; mix-blend-mode: normal; }:root{--color-primary:#073057;--color-accent:#1AAD94;--color-dark:#2C2C2C;--color-light:#F9FAFB;--color-border:#E0E0E0;--color-muted:#6B7280}body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;color:var(--color-dark);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}.hero-dot-grid{background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(26,173,148,0.15) 1.5px,transparent 1.5px);background-size:32px 32px}.compass-spin{animation:spin 60s linear infinite}@keyframes spin{from{transform:rotate(0deg)}to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}.pipeline-pulse{animation:pulse-teal 2s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.6,1) infinite}@keyframes pulse-teal{0%,100%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}50%{transform:scale(1.1);opacity:.8}}h1,h2,h3,h4{letter-spacing:-0.02em}</style></head><body><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white flex flex-col\"><nav style=\"view-transition-name: main-nav\" class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/10 bg-[#073057]/95 backdrop-blur supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-[#073057]/90\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"flex min-h-[78px] items-center justify-between gap-4\"><a style=\"view-transition-name: brand-logo\" href=\"#\" id=\"nav-brand-logo\" class=\"flex items-center gap-4 no-underline\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94] shrink-0 shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(26,173,148,0.25)]\"><span class=\"text-base font-bold tracking-widest text-white\">JCL</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col leading-tight\"><span class=\"text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-white uppercase\">JOSEOCEANJOBS</span><span class=\"text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/50\">Jose Consulting Limited</span></div></a><div class=\"hidden xl:flex items-center gap-7\"><a href=\"#\" id=\"nav-home\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">Home</a><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/dcbb8baf-c311-42eb-8c3b-01359cbbdafc\" id=\"nav-about\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">About</a><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/d2d5d0aa-c669-49b6-9b33-a28441cf4b5d\" id=\"nav-leadership\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">Leadership</a><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/254e9f8f-72d8-4ce3-a2b9-61b026d05b1e\" id=\"nav-partnerships\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">Partnerships</a><a href=\"#\" id=\"nav-jobs\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">Jobs</a><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/a44ee394-4e27-4984-95ee-689b5df446b4\" id=\"nav-contact\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">Contact</a></div><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-3\"><a href=\"#\" id=\"nav-cta-training\" class=\"inline-flex px-5 py-2.5 border border-white/20 rounded-[8px] text-white text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] hover:bg-white/10 transition-all\">Request Training</a><a href=\"#\" id=\"nav-cta-register\" class=\"inline-flex px-5 py-2.5 bg-[#1AAD94] rounded-[8px] text-white text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] hover:brightness-110 transition-all\">Start Your Pathway</a></div></div></div></nav><main style=\"view-transition-name: main-content\" class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-[#073057] py-24 lg:py-32 hero-dot-grid\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid gap-14 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center\"><div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#7DE1D1] mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:globe-2\" class=\"text-sm\"></iconify-icon><span>JOSE CONSULTING LIMITED</span></div><h1 class=\"max-w-4xl text-[56px] font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-white md:text-[72px]\">Your Career at Sea Starts Here</h1><p class=\"mt-8 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-white/70\">Empowering Skills, Connecting Worlds. We bridge the gap between talented professionals and global maritime opportunities through world-class training and consulting.</p><div class=\"mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a href=\"#\" id=\"hero-primary-cta\" class=\"inline-flex px-8 py-4 bg-[#1AAD94] rounded-[8px] text-white text-[14px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] hover:brightness-110 shadow-lg transition-all\">Start your pathway</a><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/a44ee394-4e27-4984-95ee-689b5df446b4\" id=\"hero-secondary-cta\" class=\"inline-flex px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/20 rounded-[8px] text-white text-[14px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] hover:bg-white/10 transition-all\">Contact JCL</a></div><div class=\"mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"rounded-[18px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-white\">1,200+</div><div class=\"mt-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#7DE1D1]\">Open Jobs</div></div><div class=\"rounded-[18px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-white\">85</div><div class=\"mt-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#7DE1D1]\">Partner Orgs</div></div><div class=\"rounded-[18px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-white\">24/7</div><div class=\"mt-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#7DE1D1]\">Support</div></div><div class=\"rounded-[18px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-white\">15+</div><div class=\"mt-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#7DE1D1]\">Countries</div></div></div></div><div class=\"relative hidden lg:block\"><div class=\"absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-[500px] w-[500px] rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94]/10 blur-[120px]\"></div><div class=\"relative flex justify-center items-center h-full\"><div class=\"compass-spin h-[480px] w-[480px] border border-white/5 rounded-full relative flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-dashed border-white/10\"></div><div class=\"h-[380px] w-[380px] border border-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"h-[280px] w-[280px] border border-[#1AAD94]/20 rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-md\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544620347-c4fd4a3d5957?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=400\" alt=\"Maritime Safety\" class=\"rounded-[24px] shadow-2xl h-48 w-full object-cover\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494412574743-0194849a6431?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=400\" alt=\"Deck Officer\" class=\"rounded-[24px] mt-8 shadow-2xl h-48 w-full object-cover\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white py-24\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] lg:items-center\"><div><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94]/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94] mb-6\">Workforce Transformation</div><h2 class=\"text-[48px] font-extrabold leading-tight text-[#073057]\">From readiness gaps to global opportunity.</h2><p class=\"mt-8 text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#6B7280]\">JCL exists to bridge skilled professionals with real industry pathways in the maritime and energy sectors. We combine practical training, consulting insight, and specialist partnerships to create international relevance.</p><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-[#E0E0E0] bg-[#F9FAFB] p-8 transition-all hover:border-[#1AAD94] hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-2\">4,500</div><div class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94]\">Trained Professionals</div></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-[#E0E0E0] bg-[#F9FAFB] p-8 transition-all hover:border-[#1AAD94] hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-2\">98%</div><div class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94]\">Deployment Rate</div></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-[#E0E0E0] bg-[#F9FAFB] p-8 transition-all hover:border-[#1AAD94] hover:shadow-xl\"><div class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-2\">24hr</div><div class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94]\">Average Response</div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-[#073057] p-10 text-white\"><div class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94] mb-6\">The Pathway</div><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/10 text-sm font-bold\">01</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Skill Assessment</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-white/60\">We evaluate your current certifications and technical readiness.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94] text-sm font-bold\">02</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Global Certification</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-white/60\">Bridge gaps with internationally recognized training programs.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-6\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/10 text-sm font-bold\">03</div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold\">Vessel Matching</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-white/60\">Connect with fleet operators seeking your specific skill set.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#F9FAFB] py-24\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-[32px] bg-white border border-[#E0E0E0] p-10 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden group\"><div class=\"relative z-10\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-[#073057]/5 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#073057] mb-6\">Our Vision</div><h2 class=\"text-[36px] font-extrabold text-[#073057] leading-tight mb-8\">To be the premier architect of global maritime talent pathways.</h2><ul class=\"space-y-4\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-[#2C2C2C]\"><div class=\"flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94]/10 text-[#1AAD94]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:check-circle-2\" class=\"text-lg\"></iconify-icon></div><span class=\"font-medium\">Standardizing global workforce quality</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-[#2C2C2C]\"><div class=\"flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94]/10 text-[#1AAD94]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:check-circle-2\" class=\"text-lg\"></iconify-icon></div><span class=\"font-medium\">Driving sustainable offshore growth</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-[#2C2C2C]\"><div class=\"flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94]/10 text-[#1AAD94]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:check-circle-2\" class=\"text-lg\"></iconify-icon></div><span class=\"font-medium\">Innovating in talent mobility tech</span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[32px] bg-[#073057] p-10 text-white shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute right-0 top-0 h-40 w-40 bg-white/5 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 blur-2xl\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-white/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#7DE1D1] mb-6\">Our Mission</div><h2 class=\"text-[36px] font-extrabold leading-tight mb-8\">Connecting world-class expertise to high-impact maritime roles.</h2><ul class=\"space-y-4\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-white/80\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-right\" class=\"text-[#1AAD94]\"></iconify-icon><span class=\"font-medium\">Facilitate seamless global deployments</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-white/80\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-right\" class=\"text-[#1AAD94]\"></iconify-icon><span class=\"font-medium\">Deliver benchmarked industry training</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-white/80\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-right\" class=\"text-[#1AAD94]\"></iconify-icon><span class=\"font-medium\">Ensure safety and operational excellence</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white py-24\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-16\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94]/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94] mb-6\">Leadership & Expertise</div><h2 class=\"text-[48px] font-extrabold text-[#073057]\">The minds guiding JCL.</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-[#6B7280]\">Decades of combined experience across oil and gas, maritime logistics, and global workforce consulting.</p></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-[#E0E0E0] p-8 bg-white transition-all hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 mb-8\"><div class=\"h-20 w-20 rounded-full bg-[#073057] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white shadow-xl\">JD</div><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057]\">John Doe</h3><p class=\"text-[#1AAD94] text-sm font-semibold\">Managing Director</p></div></div><p class=\"text-[#6B7280] leading-relaxed mb-6\">Specializing in global logistics and maritime strategy with 20+ years of operational excellence in offshore energy.</p><div class=\"pt-6 border-t border-[#E0E0E0] flex justify-between items-center\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[#073057]/40\">Executive</span><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[#073057] hover:text-[#1AAD94] transition-colors\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:linkedin\" class=\"text-xl\"></iconify-icon></a></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-[#E0E0E0] p-8 bg-white transition-all hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 mb-8\"><div class=\"h-20 w-20 rounded-full bg-[#073057] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white shadow-xl\">SA</div><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057]\">Sarah Adams</h3><p class=\"text-[#1AAD94] text-sm font-semibold\">Head of Training</p></div></div><p class=\"text-[#6B7280] leading-relaxed mb-6\">Certified master trainer overseeing STCW programs and technical workforce development for international fleets.</p><div class=\"pt-6 border-t border-[#E0E0E0] flex justify-between items-center\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-[#073057]/40\">Training</span><a href=\"#\" class=\"text-[#073057] hover:text-[#1AAD94] transition-colors\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:linkedin\" class=\"text-xl\"></iconify-icon></a></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-[#E0E0E0] p-8 bg-white transition-all hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 mb-8\"><div class=\"h-20 w-20 rounded-full bg-[#073057] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white shadow-xl\">MK</div><div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057]\">Marcus Kwesi</h3><p class=\"text-[#1AAD94] text-sm font-semibold\">Operations Lead</p></div></div><p class=\"text-[#6B7280] leading-relaxed mb-6\">Managing vessel mobilization and talent acquisition logistics across the West African and